{"tid":801441,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家好，我是一條矮撚，我是一個悲劇","createTime":"2018-08-31T15:37:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T13:27:58.000Z","uid":120847,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"761deaa6058c3902ce2c7e5e4b755094362bc7e2","tid":801441,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T15:37:34.000Z","msg":"在基因排序中 已埋下這悲劇的伏線<br />\n誰能明白 這小小的身軀 是多麼沉重<br />\n因為長得矮小 自小便飽受自卑症煎熬<br />\n長大後 有了一點成就 也曾享受過戀愛 <br />\n便暫且矇了眼 不再看自己矮小的事實 把自卑收起<br />\n但自卑症這魔鬼就像舊患 在人生不如意 抗逆力弱時 又悄悄地復發 摧毀我的意志<br />\n我不自覺地捲入抑鬱的漩渦 無法自拔<br />\n不要和別人親近！不要讓你的負能量傳染別人<br />\n不要結婚！不要生育下一代！不要把悲劇延續下去<br />\n宇宙，世界，本來不為我而設<br />\n既然無奈地背負這身軀來了，就唯有無奈地活下去，無奈地死去吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f8e4c9b7acf75e05980835ce7cd54ea558a3461","tid":801441,"uid":115510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T15:38:29.000Z","msg":"I know that feel"},{"pid":"2d7808fb005840d826b34ade2d6c73d88395927e","tid":801441,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f8e4c9b7acf75e05980835ce7cd54ea558a3461","tid":801441,"uid":115510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T15:38:29.000Z","msg":"I know that feel"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T15:39:10.000Z","msg":"thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"615871675c2664cf6716a649f8d205379ad8c5a9","tid":801441,"uid":32219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T15:40:48.000Z","msg":"How tall?"},{"pid":"65dc851df945831a11bc58b6eb6e70dba2eece94","tid":801441,"uid":115510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"615871675c2664cf6716a649f8d205379ad8c5a9","tid":801441,"uid":32219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T15:40:48.000Z","msg":"How tall?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T15:41:16.000Z","msg":"1.53"},{"pid":"ea1a649403f015d241c88be38e1faff583120896","tid":801441,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0